Library team members give overview of library resources as and when a new user comes in the LIRC. They interact with them to know their requirements. Time to time LIRC send library profile, how to use library resources tips at their email IDs.

LIRC provides LIRC at a glance to the new students at the time of registrations. Library members also give briefing about the LIRC services. Orientation of LIRC resources and services is also given to the users during orientation programme.